<h1 class="jazz-page-title">Typography</h1>

<p>The Design System typography allows developers to easily apply a default set of font weights, font sizes, lineheights, and letterspacings.</p>

<h2>Headings</h2>

{{ example("/design/typography/headings/heading-example1", "Demonstration", "code-panel-demo") }}

<p>
    Heading styles are pre-defined as T-Shirt sizes—<span class="code">jazz-xxl</span>, <span class="code">jazz-xl</span>, <span class="code">jazz-l</span>, <span class="code">jazz-m</span>, <span class="code">jazz-s</span>, <span class="code">jazz-xs</span>.
    Adding a T-shirt size to a heading's class will apply the pre-defined style as specified in the table below:
</p>

