<p>
    Using the pre-defined heading style will override its default styles, therefore using any one
    of the existing HTML headings—h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6—with a T-shirt size will result in a uniform appearance.
    While multiples of the same HTML heading can be used with different T-shirt sizes to simulate multiple heading styles,
    this practice is not recommended for reasons pertaining to search engine crawlers and SEO best practices. It is important
    to keep this in mind and use different heading tags in relation to its priority.
</p>

